        <span class="module-label">MODULE ONE</span>
        <h2 class="module-title">
          Setup &<br />
          Installation
        </h2>
      </header>
      
      <div class="module-intro">
        <p>Terminal basics, developer tools, and Claude Code. One-time setup, then you're ready to build.</p>
      </div>
      
